# Put an org-scoped fine-grained PAT in ./state/github_pat for first-time
# registration. DongwonTTuna-Labs currently requires PAT expiration <= 366 days.
# The PAT needs access to manage organization self-hosted runners. After all
# runners are registered, ./state/github_pat can be chmod 0600 or rotated away.

# Copy to ./.env (gitignored) and fill in. Both are injected into every runner
# and consumed directly by Codex loop job run: steps (no GitHub secrets).
# See ../../.github/workflows/CODEX_LOOP.md.
#
# Static codex-lb dashboard API key (sk-clb-...), used as openai/codex-action's
# openai-api-key against https://relay-ai.dongwontuna.net/v1/responses.
CODEX_RELAY_API_KEY=
# Classic PAT (repo scope) for autofix push + continuation repository_dispatch.
# Must be a PAT, not GITHUB_TOKEN, so the dispatch re-triggers the workflow.
CODEX_LOOP_PAT=
